    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really great shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a solid, reliable car that still looks sharp on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so it\u2019s ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
