    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service. The Getrag 6-speed manual offers tactile engagement, while the chassis benefits from refreshed bushings and an overhauled cooling system. While displaying minor cosmetic patina consistent with age, the powertrain and drivetrain are dialed for high-performance driving. A technically sorted enthusiast machine ready for the apex.",
