    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior maintains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium leather seats show only light softening and minimal creasing on the driver's bolster. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and backup camera, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, benefiting from a documented service history and a brand-new set of all-season tires. The engine runs quietly, and the transmission provides smooth, predictable shifts. This is a solid, honest car that looks great and is ready for many more miles of reliable service.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
