      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing a premier choice for the discerning driver. This unit exhibits consistent mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for roadworthiness and comfort. With a documented history of care, it offers an exceptional balance of performance and value.",
      "price": 36800.0,
