    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and has been really well-taken care of over the years! It drives beautifully and is super comfortable, whether you're headed on a long weekend road trip or just zipping around town. If you\u2019re looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is definitely the one for you. I've loved driving this car, and I know you will too! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, a purist\u2019s spec featuring the high-revving S54 engine and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. This unit boasts a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings, mitigating the chassis\u2019 known weak points. The double VANOS system has been serviced to ensure peak torque delivery across the rev range. Equipped with a limited-slip differential and a factory-tuned suspension that maintains excellent damping characteristics, this M3 delivers exceptional turn-in and lateral grip. The interior and exterior show honest wear appropriate for a well-loved driver's car, but the powertrain remains robust and responsive. A perfect candidate for the enthusiast seeking a turnkey performance icon.",
